<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَتُبَاحُ المُبَاشَرَةُ فِيمَا دُونَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالمُبْتَدَأَةُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- تَجْلِسُ أَقَلَّهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- ثُمَّ تَغْتَسِلُ وَتُصَلِّي.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ لَمْ يُجَاوِزْ دَمُهَا أَكْثَرَهُ:</span> اغْتَسَلَتْ أَيْضاً إِذَا انْقَطَعَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ تَكَرَّرَ ثَلَاثاً:</span> فَهُوَ حَيْضٌ، تَقْضِي مَا وَجَبَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَإِنْ أَيِسَتْ قَبْلَهُ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ لَمْ يَعُدْ:</span> فَلَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ جَاوَزَهُ:</span> فَمُسْتَحَاضَةٌ، تَجْلِسُ المُتَمَيِّزَ إِنْ كَانَ وَصَلُحَ فِي الشَّهْرِ الثَّانِي.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَإِلَّا أَقَلَّ الحَيْضِ حَتَّى تَتَكَرَّرَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> اسْتِحَاضتُهَا، ثُمَّ غَالِبَهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمُسْتَحَاضَةٌ مُعْتَادَةٌ:</span> تُقَدِّمُ عَادَتَهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَلْزَمُهَا وَنَحْوَهَا:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- غَسْلُ المَحَلِّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَعَصْبُهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَالوُضُوءُ لِوَقْتِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> كُلِّ صَلَاةٍ إِنْ خَرَجَ شَيْءٌ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (ب): تكرر.<br>(٢) قوله: (لوقت) سقطت من (أ) و (ب) و (ج).</p> </div>